irectors of Education are very aware of the power and benefits of parent engagement. That''s why CODE is pleased to provide this <a href="http://www.ontariodirectors.ca/Parent_Engagement/PA%20Downloads/34919_CODE_Guidebook-ENG_sm.pdf"><strong>Planning Parent Engagement Guidebook</strong></a> to accompany the Parent Tool Kit. In this Guidebook are examples of useful exercises and proven techniques for involvement and support.\n\n<strong>(For additional resources visit </strong><a href="http://www.ontariodirectors.ca/parent_engagement.html#pe5"><strong>this link</strong></a><strong>.)</strong>', 'Parent engagement resources for student success', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2357-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-03-31 01:16:01', '2015-03-31 01:16:01', '', 2357, 'http://staging.ontariosummerlearning.org/2357-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
