(2382, 1, '2015-04-14 13:14:06', '2015-04-14 13:14:06', '<h3>Once your summer program is implemented, be sure to:</h3>\n\n<ul class="ul1">\n	<li class="li2"><span class="s1">Take attendance and enter it into the spreadsheet</span></li>\n	<li class="li2"><span class="s1">Record parent and student comments that may be relevant to the teacher questionnaire</span></li>\n	<li class="li2"><span class="s1">Take photos that can be shared (make sure parents sign permission form)</span></li>\n	<li class="li2"><span class="s1">Share program details with regional lead </span></li>\n	<li class="li2"><span class="s1">Engage parents in a two-way dialogue about their child''s involvement in the SLP</span></li>\n	<li class="li2"><span class="s1">Be sure to celebrate your successes!</span></li>\n</ul>\nDon''t forget to take advantage of the great tips and tools contributed by the SLP community in the Resources section!\n<a href="http://staging.ontariosummerlearning.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/July_August_To_Do.pdf" target="_blank">Download monthly tips for July and August</a> to help with your planning.', 'Implement Your Program', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2307-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-04-14 13:14:06', '2015-04-14 13:14:06', '', 2307, 'http://staging.ontariosummerlearning.org/2307-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
