(2749, 3, '2015-08-04 00:09:27', '2015-08-04 00:09:27', '\nWe would really like to hear about your experiences using the robotics kits in the summer learning program and your feedback is very important to us. This survey is voluntary, and your information will be kept confidential. It should only take you about ten minutes to complete. The results will be used to inform an action research project on how robotics might impact teaching and learning. Your feedback will also be used to inform future planning for professional learning in your district school board. Thank you in advance for your feedback.\n\nhttp://fluidsurveys.com/s/summerlearningprogram_robotics-feedback/', 'Summer Learning Program Robotics Survey', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'summer-learning-program-robotics-survey', '', '', '2015-08-04 00:09:27', '2015-08-04 00:09:27', '', 2253, 'http://ontariosummerlearning.org/forums/topic/summer-learning-program-robotics-survey/', 0, 'topic', '', 0),
