(2758, 3, '2015-08-10 14:45:31', '2015-08-10 14:45:31', 'Welcome to the CODE robotics forum.\n\nAs part of this year’s (2015) summer learning program, 35 boards took part in a pilot project using STEM resources/robotics to further engage their students in learning, to build collaboration and extend opportunities for hands-on activities, and to connect the robotic resources to the development of literacy and numeracy skills.\n\nThis forum has been created for sharing your experiences, ideas, classroom activities and learning opportunities as a teacher or program lead involved in the STEM resources/robotics pilot project. Forum users are free to join in any topic, or start one of their own, but all discussions should relate directly to your experiences with the robotics kits and summer learning.\n\nYour participation in this forum will help inform future use of these resources in classrooms across the province, so please jump in and start posting questions, comments and suggestions on robotics and student learning. And don''t forget to complete the brief survey/report back on your experiences with the STEM resources/robotics kits this summer. The survey can be found by following this link: <a href="http://fluidsurveys.com/s/summerlearningprogram_robotics-feedback/" target="_blank">http://fluidsurveys.com/s/summerlearningprogram_robotics-feedback/</a>\n\nAnd once again, welcome to the summer learning robotics forum!', 'Welcome to the CODE robotics forum', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'welcome-to-the-code-robotics-forum', '', '', '2015-08-10 14:45:31', '2015-08-10 14:45:31', '', 2253, 'http://ontariosummerlearning.org/forums/topic/welcome-to-the-code-robotics-forum/', 0, 'topic', '', 0),
